First Department,

April, 1973

(April 3, 1973) Herman Badillo et al., Appellants, v. Herman Katz, Individually, and as City Clerk of the City of New York, et al., Respondents. John D. Calandra et al., Individually, and as County Chairmen of the Republican Party in the Boroughs of New York City, Appellants, v. David Dinkins, as Chairman of the Board of Elections, et al., Respondents.

Order, Supreme Court, Bronx County, entered on March 19, 1973, unanimously affirmed, without costs and without disbursements. The actions are remanded to the Supreme Court, Bronx County, for immediate trial. The application made by Mr. Zimmerman on argument is denied. No opinion. Concur — Stevens, P. J., Markewich, Murphy, Steuer and Capozzoli, JJ.
